.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt SQLITE3CHANGEGROUP_CHANGE_NULL 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sqlite3changegroup_change_null
.Nd add a NULL to a changegroup
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In sqlite3.h
.Ft int
.Fo sqlite3changegroup_change_null
.Fa "sqlite3_changegroup*"
.Fa "int"
.Fa "int"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
This function is similar to sqlite3changegroup_change_int64().
Except that it configures the change currently under construction with
a NULL value instead of a 64-bit integer.
.Sh IMPLEMENTATION NOTES
These declarations were extracted from the
interface documentation at line 13471.
.Bd -literal
SQLITE_API int sqlite3changegroup_change_null(sqlite3_changegroup*, int, int);
.Ed
